==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wafter
<hw>Waft"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, wafts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>O Charon,⟦br⟧
Thou <qex>wafter</qex> of the soul to bliss or bane.</q> <rj><qau>Beau.
& FL.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A boat for passage.</def>
<rj><au>Ainsworth.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wafture</ent>⟦br⟧
